{
  "stem": "9943.5",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It's in '41, in June '41, I went to Odessa.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In September-- in August, I went to Pereiaslav.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In September, I went to Syzran and from Syzran, to-- to Ufa in the-- in the fall.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "In November, I went to Tashkent.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And this is where we are now, '41.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I-- I don't think that you're going to get what you want to get from this half-hour.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I will summarize to you the whole thing so that you will-- I did work in this kolhoz two years, from '41 to '43.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I learned the Uzbek language, because otherwise it would have been medicine like animals you treated, like-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] so I learned very fast their language.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It's a Turkic group of languages.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And pretty soon, they didn't know what to do with me, really.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "[?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Was ?] treated me very well after a while, after the bad beginning and so on.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And it was- they didn't want me to leave.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They wanted me to stay there forever, and so on.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I had an interesting time, and I was only thinking about how will I to tell my-- my family what all I did and how I managed my life, and all that.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No contact whatsoever.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "No contact whatsoever.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] just was waiting.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But how will I be able to stand it to meet them?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And so I was there two years.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Then they started to-- to require doctors to go to Ukraine.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So in that-- in that [NON-ENGLISH], in Tashkent again, I have here [INAUDIBLE] some of those documents, the head of the health-- of the personnel department put me in-- they required doctors to come to Moscow.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The requirement was to come to Moscow, and then they will send me to Ukraine.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
